Simple Python utility to help you to survive in null sec space of EVE Online.
It provides intel chat log analysis and sound notification application for EVE Online.

Currently, works only on Linux :P

If you need more advanced tool, you can try https://github.com/Xanthos-Eve/vintel

Requirements:
***********************************************
python >= 3.2
pyyaml
pulseaudio (libpulse-simple.so)

Post-install:
***********************************************

You need to define your settings in the settings.yaml.
See settings_example.yaml for details.

Run tool:
***********************************************

chmod +x watcher.py
./watcher.py

* If tool can't find EVE log directory correctly:

./watcher.py <full_path_to_Chatlogs_directory>

